The paper deals with the application of convolutional neural networks (CNNs) for histology image analysis, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of transferable features and feature generalizability, which are key concepts in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of contextual information, which is relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
